Author: silvernikki
Text: I've been in a depressive binging cycle for months and felt better yesterday, so I asked my mother if she wanted to catch up. Instead of giving a simple yes or no, she came up with excuse after excuse instead of admitting that she obviously just didn't feel like seeing me. So I ate everything in my pantry. And my freezer. Because obviously I'm a terrible human being who doesn't deserve to be healthy.  Makes perfect sense!!
